  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-55bc2d37-e887-4e96-8846-b8f5dd78d00c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ebd1f3f7-951b-4e3b-a8f0-0ce674e37986\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8d83fbbd-0852-4ea4-bbaa-81698c5802c2\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 7</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7b8961ec-90fa-467b-bfab-00333aea56e7\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bc8a819e-9559-486d-9eb3-2034ef5bf61b\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6126662c-a26a-4dd2-a5ac-97645c36b33d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0020d8b6-aa17-404a-afe6-a0822b311a09\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[집중]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-83b74dfb-d17f-462f-aae2-94090ea2f64c\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e5795d2d-4875-4ced-9ce0-8d37111eb9b5\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>오늘은 (주)파파스컴퍼니 메인페이지를 완성해 보겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e3b7b182-049c-42ea-a0cd-bf0946c81b27\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6228b006-2ef2-42f8-afeb-604825594f45\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>명함이라는 카테고리와 내일은 카다로그라는 카테고리를 예시로 작성하겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ee2b28b1-3f76-4ae5-804a-f80be54a890a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4ba964b6-d199-4e46-93ae-a6a92d012d52\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니이 만들고자하는 사이트의 내용을 정리해서 작업할 예정입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c898efd8-f9e1-4885-be20-381dd3cfee86\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4cf19467-7282-4fdc-88bc-a306d3a4bdb2\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ce4ed244-57f2-4d4b-9147-4f3448afd49e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-323dd649-98a5-4304-9847-bfb4c69ad987\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-a814605f-05d0-4b31-b15e-ce4f70b232d6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-485e7c21-2f77-4ace-a6d2-9aebfd3f371c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-07844686-4a58-4a42-993d-d7bf50c639ea\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>메인페이지 요소 설명</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-75c78fc5-1961-4f72-a25c-c48a9395962d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-33323b0e-51f9-4b90-9203-b21b952b6163\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumbarungothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9f6a2db5-8fa2-4f1a-b8c2-f21d490bab54\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 메인페이지의 내용을 하나하나 설명합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8c978e5e-ff0c-446e-b33a-660ae093f9d5\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-16e995df-f90c-424a-953e-c0ee6f328d97\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-77db26d7-775e-4341-85b4-b102602d0dc0\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-de0d905b-3a47-4b38-adc8-d53b706ddd1f\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f49132f0-290b-4d3e-8ec8-5e61c5a589de\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a1c96ba1-5f6b-471a-a390-4bfba639e758\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1addb838-b148-4686-87c5-e6b08c1d34b6\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-418a63f2-b676-4ead-b234-c46f832c705d\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>본격적으로 메인페이지 스토리보딩을 시작하겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b1d689df-d6a3-4216-94a1-1a327c090c0a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\" style=\"max-width:624px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222885519415/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-db8e6d27-687c-489d-ad9e-2e4d1796d35f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-554a5ce5-1f60-499d-ad0e-1b87fecadf4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-76e12c49-123b-4ed1-b075-7a75d6a64d48\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1379a385-0806-4420-b1b9-7dbdb37ae740\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222885519415/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fe1ebaa2-6e6c-4592-baa0-38d9266afa0d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9c08f812-75ab-4985-aade-98ad463ff11b\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-764231e8-d292-495a-8267-364cda14a3c5\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>로고 자리입니다.​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2fd0a1c3-6317-4a23-aa72-45d72a3bac8e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-05c41106-7aa3-4d30-b4f9-fec887f44ec6\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 부분은 관리자페이지에서 로고를 등록하고 변경할 수 있는 페이지가 있어야 합니다. 몰론 (주)파파스컴퍼니 사이트만 개발한다면 하드코딩으로 퍼블리싱해도 충분합니다. 저는 다른 인쇄회사의 사이트를 개발해 줄 수도 있다는 생각으로 로고를 관리하는 페이지를 만들 예정입니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-887a3955-6a2a-447c-a293-9da951a4340a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ce4ab95b-57cf-496a-9f4a-c6b9ddd352db\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dfbc9b19-1563-4fe8-8978-5dd354be5006\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222885519415/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-55fa22c0-e4ce-419e-b4d0-977d327ddb49\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-203091cc-5572-44ca-ab5b-26e5edf11984\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-09aa7678-73bf-4d88-be9e-0bf5c0f5fc26\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>검색 자리입니다.​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4c0e361b-8177-45ad-af01-3bfe64240a09\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-328f7c18-980a-47ba-9d22-215621976396\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">검색은 태그나 기타 업로드 페이지에 등록된 부분을 검색기능 통해 자연어 검색을 기본으로 합니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-17361a71-282c-42ef-8294-b07fdff4f550\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1f507ca9-826f-4390-bce8-d95ff5b13002\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5e152d52-31b0-45e6-8139-da4062da9d62\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222885519415/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3ed5f837-bfe6-499c-acd1-a3ae29325088\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f7b4d582-0608-4934-a346-a2ce452a7a61\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-66e68e9a-0466-4bf0-ab81-daa077fe110e\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>메뉴 서치 자리입니다.​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c66c3ee2-d7cf-4a0b-a422-4d9ded67bb10\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b8eeaf06-4d5d-48c7-a3a6-1ff5187aa20f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 부분은 3가지를 빠르게 서칭할 수 있는 기능을 넣겠습니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4e7e7efe-dae8-41be-9016-07d1cabb394d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6481f15b-e25e-41ba-8971-ac94895c834f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">- 전체 / - 내 찜 / - 내 디자인 / - 문의 (추후 더 디테일한 내용을 정리하겠습니다. 좋은 의견 있으면 댓글 주세요.~^^)</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0fb841c3-a23c-48a0-a05b-ff78d9b05791\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a3b52e91-adf8-45a6-82cb-8aaf90b6dc39\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7b37e6c2-77c8-4614-a363-db856a10d886\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222885519415/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-004276c1-41e7-468f-874a-5b99a23f260d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-2886ea27-6ee0-498b-a33f-233169879878\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0e570263-11f2-447d-8072-a8631580ec58\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>알림 자리입니다.​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c40bbb6a-e87a-42da-8d5d-c2381f2019b0\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f03886dc-d098-4d0d-b01a-3ac29c7aac41\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">알림은 숫자로 표시되며 (주)파파스컴퍼니의 공지나 알림을 수신허용했을 때 표시될 수 있습니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c49e4d52-763f-499d-986d-3deecd63ab8b\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-83f64fb9-f455-4ddb-ba70-a6fc1da4962a\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">알림은 내가 주문한 상황의 상태나 요청을 확인할 수 있는 페이지입니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니 사이트는 마이페이지 기능을 축소(?)했습니다. 알림을 통해 주문에 대한 정보등을 수신할 수 있습니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-47a3812b-ae88-4f1d-a81c-e6e4db965cf9\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ae70fafe-a5db-4a23-8d9e-7f2bfb48c9de\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e747567b-ec40-4af2-ac2b-f413debe6f12\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222885519415/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-68798f66-2274-427a-b1df-6c57ab4543de\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-94c75bb0-1a11-421b-8abe-4715e2f74def\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6cad7f7d-dc50-4fb9-ad59-f000bfc1db65\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>마이페이지 아이콘입니다.​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9d3f151e-033e-4a49-ae73-e68dc01b62ea\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f57de960-5c8e-424c-b68c-ac87253f902e\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">마이페이지 기능은</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6a3281c4-ca3e-4b91-9e96-23d95a020a5b\" style=\"line-height:1.8