style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222885519415/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bb0f251a-de19-4785-8211-7bb18398ace1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-5f14f8bf-c6c0-4070-9748-affeba3a6ecd\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-538e63c3-70a2-4cfa-b00a-923019bb8a25\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이미지영역입니다.​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b7ffa313-5f3e-493f-be6c-e29fb2ffaed0\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d78dbb1d-0931-4420-8269-2e75c98e513c\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">디자인 이미지영역입니다. 가로폭은 픽스이고 세로(높이)는 가변입니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-bb36da94-8049-43bd-be74-dffd3b090c3f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ec4226ce-c0e3-430e-8404-f0bad3759d29\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">모바일에서 두줄정도 표시되게 가로를 픽스합니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9f412f5b-c5fc-4e17-87b0-c7cf3dfdd7e7\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4829b829-dbdb-40e8-b4c1-fa1e93ae41c2\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">관리자페이지에 디자인을 업로드하는 페이지를 만듭니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-be07fa18-6454-4cf5-9383-622621836d91\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-676ce385-6382-460b-a8b4-8e37302c9d44\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">노출허용과 비허용을 구분하여 관리합니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7c186448-5d42-48e0-abca-e303c116861e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-be637b2e-a647-443c-90c8-81d85a6d5e53\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">이미지해상도 자동 조정 기능을 넣습니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-526ebdf3-5a6d-4fd3-b9d2-8a44f7b87bba\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8cab7a7e-7068-43f4-bd48-c7df2cfb4a07\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d3ef6a84-186f-441d-9069-de14df7c1c23\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222885519415/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7ca015a7-c173-4082-9910-2e36e72531a1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-553bff32-b2e3-4f22-9dfd-66e6ab0f607b\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3b9c5cb2-885b-48a4-9633-042e52d02d85\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이미지에 대한 정보를 표시하는 영역입니다.​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9f6f79cc-0ee1-42d2-a844-a5a6a7e76529\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3549f2f7-b47a-419f-9297-f2df054f51ce\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">여기에는 태그중심으로 노출여부를 결정합니다. 예를들어</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-53804366-1137-49e1-b92a-3996fa702227\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-412dfad9-f3ac-4b35-8f9f-e20b4ad0ecf6\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">명함, 스티커등의 카테고리가 될 수 있고</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a536645b-5766-4d7a-a365-8c5366b624d4\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ac9e3198-06a7-448d-bf75-920d9b9f5ad0\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">더 디테일하게 3단 리플렛, 은박명함등으로 표시될 수 있으며</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-570569dd-44b8-4a48-8ccd-d2f9a9418592\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a2084761-4066-4d62-9183-b681282218d3\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니, 명X병원, 교X 등 거래처명이 노출될 수 있고</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1b09b60f-85e5-4e7e-8c39-0f73e950fc4a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a7c164c3-2ed2-4315-bac0-559552f65bee\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">두꺼운, 펄, 라운드등 구분이 되는 성질을 표시할 수 있습니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ec49c6f7-30e9-4fe1-9bc8-98e65a528252\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4d29d59a-2070-422b-98ca-e13bb8fc8e6e\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ca6c639b-1f6b-4f77-b78a-bf62839c59d3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222885519415/010.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0dd09c29-6d5c-4e38-8e36-5ec59bafc7aa\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-43cb243b-da7e-454d-8df4-73099fa47e12\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-37b3d476-a5bf-4030-ba55-92fd1d74b59c\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이미지에 대한 기능을 표시하는 영역입니다.​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-335a5480-acc8-43bf-8b47-b60c1bb10e2e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-863e446c-c111-4b6a-bef6-441b5fb43185\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">이미지를 어떻게 하겠다는 이벤트를 표시하는 영역입니다. 예를들어</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-767a87de-b1d4-4655-8380-898fc4640b9f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a5bc34d0-999b-4d67-a0c9-174d22d96614\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">이미지 찜</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4a0f10c2-f6ec-49bd-a573-d8fd88b3d942\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ed9e7edb-402a-4875-900a-10fb99b8dc2f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">이미지 다운로드</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a37edd8f-f8d8-4dbd-aeee-f8b82df57313\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1565b7a7-2aa3-4b06-ac04-26ef39afff13\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">이미지 숨기기</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-dd354dbf-810d-40ee-a5ff-447ef61c8ba8\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-401b6894-c83a-4eb3-a3de-433f85b23dd8\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">이미지 댓글</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4c818c30-a41d-4b6d-9d28-f6dfc762b728\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cd0972ae-396c-4537-9f7d-eb085b6504ca\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">기능에 대한 이벤트를 작동할 수 있는 페이지입니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-cd1f62f3-0b0a-4ebe-810f-c462b0187860\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-90588d2e-0299-442a-85df-d4350ae089de\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">반드시 반응형일때 모바일도 고려하는 디자인이 되어야 합니다.</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-cdc81629-a73c-471a-9abb-c2bee4ddec73\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-61ad032a-3609-4a07-b499-1fc87985aa53\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2e6548ff-e09e-4db3-8c53-aa1a8b6f355f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:37px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222885519415/011.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8ec66de8-f3a6-44ee-a477-828136ba8a26\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-71665e2d-28ab-420a-9d4d-b5746760756a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e5fe3948-ff32-4ece-ad1c-1d2e104032c7\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>푸터를 표시하는 영역입니다.​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-38761c1f-7c34-4daf-8197-fb88060335be\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4a082fc6-4a75-486d-b4be-8d705912cd83\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">개발을 위해 이 푸터도 하드코딩이 아닌 관리자에 관리하도록 개발합니다. 저는 이 사이트를 개발하여 인쇄업체에 저렴(?)한 비용으로 개발을 수주받아 개발해 드릴 예정입니다.~^^</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-15de1fe8-8158-4d95-a241-26e28eaddb56\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cc02abda-b8bd-4d5e-a06b-9cf205295a57\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-fae23f9c-84b0-4c3b-a6ff-420f1be5ca52\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-862b4e4c-5b1a-406e-89c0-a9ce4e6a7ad5\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-714d9bdc-7757-4c05-91e1-66e6ea640c00\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e4840722-da19-4361-9072-2232c60ae0f7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81e95d7f-53a7-4195-9dd2-5a7da40fac30\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>다음 글의 내용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-de254cd8-332a-421d-adae-c99ac11012df\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1448fa98-bb00-4a8d-b830-7a62bd9f5079\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7ac7d7c8-ce77-44f2-9fb5-1e0e03a4d5ab\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[기획] 명함 주문페이지 예로 모바일까지 확장해서 설명합니다. 반응형의 기본​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b777da74-d271-47b8-bd8d-9b9144b61279\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-144a3788-8a68-444c-95b7-086bb9f1c1cc\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9b9fc916-671f-4560-92af-8c4c6d319b85\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fc2606cb-5072-4307-bd78-cb8cd9f0d7eb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">반응형 개발의 기본을 모바일까지 확장하여 설명합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9f5b7ab4-0714-4f39-ab34-6cd320129b5c\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d2a71471-1513-49df-97d1-aa7e36b8d783\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-68ec8884-ab19-4bfb-b003-18488110988d\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1f0c4f19-9830-4de0-9b2d-2a82e75b13df\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e2b46168-dfee-4660-b51e-5cf061dc10e5\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-91692cc5-9ab9-4909-be70-2f12420bc023\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1e2db63c-ca92-491d-aa58-3967604c70ce\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222885519415/012.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fc884abe-2d38-4fbe-a93d-fffb81cbd063\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0c004758-a900-4309-8df0-9f28c641a1e3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f07fbacb-4b90-4d70-91dc-e0523dc643a8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
